title: Preview: Texas Tech Invitational - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Preview: Texas Tech Invitational - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: LUBBOCK, Texas – The Red Raiders continue a three-week home stretch this weekend, hosting Tulsa and Texas A&M- Corpus Christi in the Texas Tech Invitational Saturday, March 12 and Sunday, March 13 at Rocky Johnson Field.
